OL,3,CMr Bates vs The Post Office: The Drama
OL,4,CThat Shocked Britain
OL,6,FThe wrongful conviction of hundreds of
OL,7,FPost Office workers due to faulty
OL,8,Fsoftware has been one of Britain's
OL,9,Fbiggest miscarriages of justice.
OL,10,FTwenty five years on from the first
OL,11,Fconvictions for theft and fraud, it
OL,12,Fhas taken the ITV drama Mr Bates vs
OL,13,FThe Post Office to ignite mass public
OL,14,Finterest in the scandal.
