OL,6,FThe program also speaks to a number of
OL,7,Fpeople involved behind the scenes in
OL,8,Fthe Mr Bates Vs The Post Office drama,
OL,9,Fincluding Ben Gale and Natasha Bondy
OL,10,Ffrom Little Gem Media, who co-produced
OL,11,Fthe series with ITV Studios and
OL,12,FDirector James Strong (Mr Bates Vs The
OL,13,FPost Office / Vigil).
OL,15,FTonight, Paul Brand reports on the
OL,16,Fimpact of the drama, and asks why has
OL,17,Fjustice for these postal workers taken
OL,18,Fso long?
