OL,6,FPaul meets Jo Hamilton, one of
OL,7,Fhundreds of subpostmasters who were
OL,8,Fprosecuted over claims they were
OL,9,Fstealing from the Post Office and who
OL,10,Fwas portrayed in the drama by Monica
OL,11,FDolan. Jo says: "Nobody expected it to
OL,12,Fdo as well as it has. I think it's
OL,13,Fstruck a chord that we all feel a bit
OL,14,Funheard in this country at the moment,
OL,15,Fnobody listens to you. What they've
OL,16,Fdone to all of us is so wicked."
OL,18,FWe also filmed with Lee Castleton and
OL,19,FWill Mellor, who played Lee in the
OL,20,Fdrama. Will says:
