OL,6,F"To be honest, I didn't know much
OL,7,Fabout the post office scandal at all
OL,8,Fbefore I got offered the role. It was
OL,9,Fsomething that I'd heard people talk
OL,10,Fabout. I'd seen it in the press a
OL,11,Flittle bit, but I couldn't imagine how
OL,12,Fbig it was, uh, until I'd seen the
OL,13,Fscript."
OL,15,F"Playing the real person is such a
OL,16,Fresponsibility that comes with that.
OL,17,FBecause you wanna make sure you get it
OL,18,Fright? And you think they're gonna be
OL,19,Fwatching this."
