OL,6,FJames says: "I mean we thought we
OL,7,Fwould raise awareness of the issue. We
OL,8,Fthought we would help get it to a
OL,9,Fwider audience. I don't think anybody
OL,10,Fever thought within a week it would be
OL,11,Fbeing raised in parliament and that
OL,12,Fsomething tangible would be happening."
OL,14,FThis isn't the first time TV has made
OL,15,Fsuch an impact. In 1996, ITV made a
OL,16,Fdrama about Hillsborough. Ian McBride
OL,17,Fwas the co-executive producer.
