OL,3,CMr Bates vs The Post Office: The Drama
OL,4,CThat Shocked Britain
OL,6,F"The impact of Hillsborough, the film,
OL,7,Fwas enormous. Its journalism uncovered
OL,8,Fall sorts of things which had
OL,9,Fpreviously been unknown and yet were
OL,10,Fmuch later shown to be absolutely
OL,11,Ftrue. So what we did, what we set out
OL,12,Fto do and succeeded beyond our
OL,13,Fexpectations was giving people a voice
OL,14,Fthat had been denied a voice."
