OL,6,FChristopher Eccelstone played Trevor
OL,7,FHicks in the drama, whose two
OL,8,Fdaughters died at Hillsborough on that
OL,9,Fday. Christoper says "I get very
OL,10,Femotional when I talk about the whole
OL,11,Fthing. I've always believed in the
OL,12,Fpower of television. My impression was
OL,13,Fthat it changed hearts and minds."
OL,15,FWriter and showrunner Russell T Davis
OL,16,Fsays: "I think part of the reason for
OL,17,Fthis success is that not many of us
OL,18,Fare postmasters. Not many of us have,
OL,19,Fhave been in this situation. But
OL,20,Factually, don't you all feel the
OL,21,Fsystem is against you these days."
